<section id="tabs" class="l-wrapper top-margin">
  <h2>Tabs</h2>
  <p>This section illustrates the functionality of Teleflora's tabs and how they are used to navigate through content. The image max-height in the tabs is 220px high, while max-width is contingent on the tabs container width.</p>

  <!-- TABS + FLORIST TIPS container -->
  <div id="pdpTabs" class="m-pdp-tabs pdp-tabs top-margin" style="display:block;">
